import React from 'react'
import { FaGithub, FaReact, FaLinkedIn, FaMedium } from 'react-icons/fa6'

export default function Icon( { icon, size = '1.5rem', color = 'black' }) {
    
    let IconComponent;

    switch (icon) {
        case 'Github':
            IconComponent = FaGithub
            break
        case 'LinkedIn':
            IconComponent = FaLinkedIn
            break
        case 'Email':
            IconComponent = FaRegEnvelope
            break
        case 'Medium':
            IconComponent = FaMedium
            break
        default:
            IconComponent = FaReact
            break
    }

    return <IconComponent size={size} color={color} />
}
